library("gganimate")
library("RColorBrewer")
library("transformr")

dados <- read.csv("./SRAGs-tabela-last-updated_revised3.csv", as.is = TRUE)
dt.plot <- reshape2::melt(dados)
## Using Data as id variables
dt.plot$Data <- as.Date(dt.plot$Data, format = "%d/%m/%Y")
dt.plot$variable <- as.Date(gsub("X", "", dt.plot$variable), format = "%d.%m.%y")

# Setting locale to Brasil
Sys.setlocale(category = "LC_TIME", locale = "pt_BR.UTF-8")
## [1] "pt_BR.UTF-8"
nowc <-
    ggplot(data = dt.plot) +
    geom_line(aes(x = Data, y = value, colour = factor(variable)), size = 2) +
    #geom_text(x = "2020-05-01", y = 250, label = "Data da Base: {frame_time}") +
    scale_x_date(date_labels = "%d/%B") +
    scale_colour_viridis_d(direction = -1) +
    labs(x = "Data do Óbito", y = "Número de Óbitos", colour = "Data da Base", title = "Evolução de Óbitos por Data de Óbito", caption = "Fonte: Boletins Epidemiológicos do Ministério da Saúde") +
    theme_cowplot() +
    theme(legend.position = "none",
          plot.title = element_text(hjust = 0.5, size = 22),
          plot.subtitle = element_text(hjust = 0.5, size = 18),
          axis.text.x = element_text(size = 16),
          axis.text.y = element_text(size = 16),
          axis.title.x = element_text(size = 18, face = "bold"),
          axis.title.y = element_text(size = 18, face = "bold"),) +
    transition_states(factor(variable)) +
    shadow_mark(colour = "lightgrey", alpha = 0.5, size = 1)

animate(nowc,
        duration = 25,
        end_pause = 5,
        width = 800,
        height = 800)
